"... Do they suit me?"[l][r]
I rapidly blinked, processing the sight before me. My glasses were too big for her, and the look she gave me while wearing them... I couldn't bear being stared up at like that any longer.[l][r]
I was utterly defeated. There wasn't anything I could've done but to start laughing.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

