"Pfft—ahaha..."[l][r]
"What? Do they not suit me?"[l][r]
"No no no, absolutely not... c'mon, give them back. They’re too big for you."[l][r]
"Well, <i>I</i> thought they looked good."[r]
"<i>Please</i> make sure you get the right size at the store," I chuckled a little more before wiping a tear off my eye, continuing.[l][r]
"Ah... pulling a stunt just like Yuuri would..."[l][r]
"What?"[r]
"You’ve been acting a lot like her lately," I teased as my lips curled into a playful grin.[l][r]
"Wh—... No way...!"[r]
"Whaaat, are you happy about it?"[l][r]
"No."[r]
"Exactly."[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

