Chito grumbled with furrowed brows and a disgusted expression, and I just nodded my head; but then we looked at each other, saw each other's faces, and started giggling madly.[l][r]
I hear someone apologize for being late not too far away, but...[r]
... we were too busy splitting our sides to reply, our shoulders shaking in unison.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

