"There’s no way it's fine..." A tremble in my voice slipped past the iron grip I held it in.[l] Chito stayed completely silent, however; had she anticipated that I'd react this way?[l][r]
[r]"Don't bottle your emotions up like that! If you keep going this way, then one day... one day..."[r]
I put in the hardest effort to force more words out of myself, to say more than I have, but I choked.[l][r]
Because my voice started to crack up. Because my tears were about to spill out.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

